annotationA: Anaphase-promoting complex subunit 10; Component of the anaphase promoting complex/cyclosome (APC/C), a cell cycle-regulated ubiquitin ligase that controls progression through mitosis and the G1 phase of the cell cycle
annotationB: Lemming B (LmgB) is part of the dicistronic lemming locus with two open reading frames (ORFs): lmgA (upstream ORF) and lmgB (downstream ORF). The lmgB ORF codes for a putative polypeptide of 365 amino acids that appears to be conserved in Drosophilidae but not in other species
